1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:52,540
=Episode 15=
(Report Letter)

3
00:02:53,020 --> 00:03:03,020
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

4
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:04,730
Han Ning,

5
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:06,170
pass me my dialysis bag.

6
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,010
Hold on,

7
00:03:10,010 --> 00:03:11,060
here's a letter for you.

8
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:14,660
(To: Gao Songge)

9
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,660
(Want to make some extra cash?)

10
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:27,220
(Fengyang Police Station, Jiangbin Municipal PSB)
(Just do as I say.)

11
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:29,570
(Don't let anyone see the bottles.)

12
00:03:29,570 --> 00:03:30,500
(Bring the empty ones)

13
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:32,540
(back to me next time.)

14
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:33,660
(If you break the rules,)

15
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:34,570
(you're out for good.)

16
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:37,010
Who delivered this?

17
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:38,770
The post office
dropped it off this morning.

18
00:03:39,450 --> 00:03:40,290
What's wrong?

19
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:42,290
Nothing.

20
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:46,890
Songge, are you packed?

21
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:48,340
Let's go.

22
00:03:48,690 --> 00:03:49,940
I can go by myself.

23
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:51,130
The cafe will get busy soon,

24
00:03:51,130 --> 00:03:53,090
and we can't
leave Han Ning to run it all alone.

25
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:58,100
(Confirm)

26
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:00,260
You get back to work.

27
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:01,540
I'll just take a cab over.

28
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,780
Be careful then.

29
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:04,620
I'm off.

30
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:10,020
(Yingxiong Web Cafe)

31
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:11,180
Hui.

32
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:13,130
Did you get your family stuff sorted?

33
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:14,970
When do we start?

34
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:16,980
Soon.

35
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,540
I contacted my downline.

36
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:20,500
Don't lie to me.

37
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:23,100
Or I might get a might ruthless.

38
00:04:26,490 --> 00:04:27,330
Tomorrow,

39
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:29,250
you'll get a final answer.

40
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:32,100
Even if we keep doing this,

41
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,250
you need to give me time

42
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:34,370
to come up with a plan.

43
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:36,780
Don't play games with me.

44
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:56,290
We've been looking all over for you.

45
00:04:56,290 --> 00:04:57,660
And here you are, chilling.

46
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:59,850
Qiang. Long.

47
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:01,340
Have a seat.

48
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:02,460
You should know

49
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,340
why we're here.

50
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:04,370
What did I do?

51
00:05:04,370 --> 00:05:05,540
Playing dumb, huh?

52
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,050
Let me jog your memory.

53
00:05:07,050 --> 00:05:08,220
Last Friday.

54
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:09,170
Jinxiu Club.

55
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:11,620
Think about it.

56
00:05:23,410 --> 00:05:24,260
Excuse me, sir.

57
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,140
Another customer

58
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,490
asked me to pass this along to you.

59
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:27,650
He also asked me to say,

60
00:05:27,650 --> 00:05:28,570
"Have a safe trip."

61
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,020
Alright, thank you.

62
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,300
(126 Fanyu Road)

63
00:05:56,450 --> 00:05:57,290
Hello?

64
00:05:57,910 --> 00:05:58,860
Hey, Hai.

65
00:05:59,370 --> 00:06:01,050
Did you receive

66
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:01,890
my parting gift?

67
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:04,370
How did you find out

68
00:06:04,370 --> 00:06:05,220
about this address?

69
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:08,100
Of course I know.

70
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:09,810
What are you doing? What's going on?

71
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:10,730
You know exactly

72
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:11,980
what you've done.

73
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,670
126 Fanyu Road.

74
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,000
It looks like a club,

75
00:06:15,010 --> 00:06:16,700
but you know exactly

76
00:06:16,700 --> 00:06:17,660
what's hiding in there.

77
00:06:19,460 --> 00:06:20,810
If you haven't left the city

78
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:22,340
by tomorrow morning,

79
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,930
the police will seize the stash

80
00:06:24,930 --> 00:06:26,930
at your warehouse.

81
00:06:26,930 --> 00:06:28,220
And when that happens,

82
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:30,290
you really will lose everything.

83
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:31,410
Are you threatening me?

84
00:06:31,410 --> 00:06:32,410
Right back at you,

85
00:06:32,410 --> 00:06:33,250
Hai.

86
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:34,770
By the way,

87
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,700
that bottle of liquor is expensive.

88
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:38,700
I couldn't even
bring myself to drink it.

89
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:39,610
So, enjoy it for me.

90
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:08,180
(Want to make some extra cash?
Just do as I say.)

91
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:37,170
Hello, Jiangbin City Paging Station.

92
00:07:37,170 --> 00:07:38,290
Operator 18 at your service.

93
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:39,250
What number will it be?

94
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:41,290
Page 3546987.

95
00:07:41,290 --> 00:07:42,290
Call this number back.

96
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,190
Understood.

97
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,040
Please hold.

98
00:08:06,170 --> 00:08:07,010
Who is this?

99
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:10,220
My husband told me to contact you.

100
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,610
He has a message for you.

101
00:08:11,610 --> 00:08:12,450
What is it?

102
00:08:12,970 --> 00:08:14,370
That day at Fengyang Police Station,

103
00:08:14,370 --> 00:08:15,370
he recognized you.

104
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:18,810
He wants you to have
100,000 yuan ready for me.

105
00:08:18,810 --> 00:08:20,020
Otherwise,

106
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,490
he'll rat you out in the prison.

107
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:24,570
Are you going to pay up?

108
00:08:28,290 --> 00:08:29,730
You lost me there.

109
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:30,570
Scar-face,

110
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,340
you can stop pretending.

111
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:34,130
If you don't agree to this,

112
00:08:34,130 --> 00:08:35,610
you and your boyfriend

113
00:08:35,610 --> 00:08:36,940
can both wait to get locked up.

114
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:42,300
Give me some time to get it ready.

115
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:01,770
Hongbing and me

116
00:09:01,770 --> 00:09:03,650
can't be with Hui forever.

117
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:04,820
If Hui is left all alone

118
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,100
to carry such a heavy burden,

119
00:09:06,530 --> 00:09:07,370
when the time comes,

120
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:10,370
how could Hongbing and me rest in peace?

121
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,580
I owe your whole family.

122
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:14,700
I won't let Chen Hui get hurt.

123
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:15,770
Even if it kills me.

124
00:09:18,530 --> 00:09:20,300
What is it? What are you looking at?

125
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,140
Nothing.

126
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:26,090
Chen Hui.

127
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:28,490
Do you think there's such a thing

128
00:09:28,490 --> 00:09:30,010
as karmic justice?

129
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:32,700
Why do you ask?

130
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,420
I've been thinking a lot lately.

131
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:37,980
Do you think karma

132
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,580
is finally catching up with us?

133
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:42,850
If there really was karma,

134
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,770
why'd you get so sick
at such a young age?

135
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,130
Maybe

136
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:55,010
this is just my fate.

137
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:58,940
Maybe that's part of karma too.

138
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:01,980
What's wrong with you?

139
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,610
You are acting strange.

140
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:05,260
It's nothing.

141
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:08,100
I just wonder sometimes.

142
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:11,340
What if we're just
not meant to beat fate?

143
00:10:13,770 --> 00:10:15,130
I think you're overthinking it.

144
00:10:15,130 --> 00:10:16,770
Look at our lives.

145
00:10:16,770 --> 00:10:18,610
Aren't things slowly getting better?

146
00:10:19,850 --> 00:10:21,250
There's no problem we can't solve.

147
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:25,420
But what if

148
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:26,820
the things we did in the past

149
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:28,850
come back to haunt us?

150
00:10:28,850 --> 00:10:29,890
What would you do?

151
00:10:32,490 --> 00:10:34,220
We worked so hard to get what we have.

152
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,490
I won't let anyone take it away.

153
00:10:59,100 --> 00:10:59,940
Hello?

154
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:01,580
I have the money ready.

155
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,840
Hello?

156
00:11:06,130 --> 00:11:07,610
Can you hear me?

157
00:11:09,490 --> 00:11:10,420
Today at 2:00 PM.

158
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:13,010
On the bridge
west of the Litou Village railway.

159
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,170
Hello?

160
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:26,420
Hai, our warehouse was
raided by the police!

161
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,980
The funds in our accounts are frozen!

162
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:29,420
Mao and the others were arrested!

163
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,420
What?

164
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:33,220
I barely managed to escape.

165
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,460
What do we do now, Hai?

166
00:12:43,610 --> 00:12:45,130
Darn you, Hui!

167
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:49,130
Mail this out for me.

168
00:12:49,130 --> 00:12:50,370
Hello, sir. What was that?

169
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:52,340
Send it out for me!

170
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:53,180
Right away, sir.

171
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:43,820
Who is it?

172
00:13:47,130 --> 00:13:48,580
Chen Hui, you set me up!

173
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,490
Didn't you?

174
00:13:49,490 --> 00:13:50,460
What do you mean?

175
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:51,580
My warehouse in Jin'gang

176
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:53,010
got raided by the cops today.

177
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:54,300
Don't play dumb!

178
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:56,130
You were careless.

179
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:57,220
It's not my fault.

180
00:13:57,550 --> 00:14:00,010
You threatened to report me yesterday,

181
00:14:00,010 --> 00:14:01,300
and today my warehouse is gone.

182
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,220
Let me tell you,

183
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:04,130
if I get caught, you're going down too.

184
00:14:04,130 --> 00:14:05,700
That's why I told you to run!

185
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:07,060
My dad has seen you.

186
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:07,940
If you don't run now,

187
00:14:07,940 --> 00:14:09,180
you won't get another chance.

188
00:14:09,180 --> 00:14:10,130
Where can I go?

189
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:11,530
I can't go back to Jin'gang,

190
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:12,820
and I can't stay here.

191
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:14,610
You're forcing my hand, Chen Hui.

192
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:15,580
I'm forcing your hand?

193
00:14:16,650 --> 00:14:18,300
You forced me to keep selling.

194
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:19,720
You even threatened me at my house!

195
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:21,220
If I hadn't helped that night,

196
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:22,820
you'd be locked up already.

197
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:23,730
You deserved

198
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:24,700
to get raided!

199
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:27,010
It really was you two.

200
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:31,850
Officer Liu.

201
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:34,420
What about us?

202
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:36,580
The ones

203
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,580
selling cough syrup in Fengyang

204
00:14:39,850 --> 00:14:41,730
were you and Hui.

205
00:14:43,100 --> 00:14:44,770
Who told you that, Officer Liu?

206
00:14:46,610 --> 00:14:48,820
Director Chen has
suspected you all along.

207
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,060
And I kept hoping

208
00:14:52,490 --> 00:14:53,580
that he was wrong.

209
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:57,460
What are you talking about, Officer Liu?

210
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,180
If there's nothing else,

211
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:01,100
I'll be going now.

212
00:15:02,850 --> 00:15:03,690
Give it back!

213
00:15:17,220 --> 00:15:19,610
Carrying cash isn't
against the law, right?

214
00:15:19,610 --> 00:15:21,060
I'm not a cop anymore.

215
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,580
I just wanted to confirm something.

216
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:28,980
If there's nothing else,

217
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:29,980
I really have to go.

218
00:15:32,180 --> 00:15:33,940
Songge!

219
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:35,370
You still have a chance, Songge.

220
00:15:35,370 --> 00:15:37,010
Come with me and turn yourself in.

221
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:38,100
- Let go of me, Officer Liu!
- Songge!

222
00:15:38,100 --> 00:15:39,700
Songge!

223
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,540
Let go!

224
00:15:55,610 --> 00:15:57,370
Let me take you to the hospital.

225
00:15:58,650 --> 00:15:59,610
It's no use.

226
00:16:02,010 --> 00:16:03,180
My time...

227
00:16:04,610 --> 00:16:05,890
is almost up.

228
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:10,770
I just wanted to help Director Chen

229
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:13,180
before I'm gone.

230
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:20,580
I want to help you too.

231
00:16:25,850 --> 00:16:27,420
You couldn't stay put in Jin'gang.

232
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,370
You just had to push me!

233
00:16:28,370 --> 00:16:29,820
You had it coming!

234
00:16:30,420 --> 00:16:31,260
Alright then.

235
00:16:31,770 --> 00:16:32,980
I'm taking you down with me!

236
00:16:35,010 --> 00:16:36,250
My money is gone.

237
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:37,210
I can't go home either.

238
00:16:37,210 --> 00:16:38,300
You won't let me live?

239
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:39,740
Then none of us gets to live!

240
00:17:14,770 --> 00:17:16,090
Even if you kill me,

241
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:18,860
that report letter will still be sent.

242
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:20,730
I never wanted to kill anyone.

243
00:17:20,730 --> 00:17:21,980
It was you guys.

244
00:17:21,980 --> 00:17:23,420
It was you!

245
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:24,980
You just kept pushing me!

246
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:27,570
You pushed me again and again!

247
00:17:27,570 --> 00:17:28,940
You won't let me live,

248
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:31,090
and you won't let Songge live!

249
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,540
Hai?

250
00:18:22,220 --> 00:18:23,060
Hai?

251
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:03,700
Songge.

252
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:07,010
Whether you admit it or not,

253
00:19:07,010 --> 00:19:08,980
the police are already
investigating this case.

254
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:11,250
You still have a choice right now.

255
00:19:12,530 --> 00:19:13,700
Turn yourself in.

256
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:18,050
Songge,

257
00:19:18,050 --> 00:19:20,330
have you thought
about Chen Hui's father?

258
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:25,010
In your life,

259
00:19:26,250 --> 00:19:27,490
are Chen Hui's parents

260
00:19:27,490 --> 00:19:29,010
important to you?

261
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:33,740
Of course.

262
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:35,900
They are like my own parents.

263
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:40,380
You should know

264
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:43,050
that here in Fengyang,

265
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:44,860
Chen Hui's grandfather

266
00:19:46,090 --> 00:19:47,940
was a hero admired by everyone.

267
00:19:49,490 --> 00:19:50,860
Since he was young,

268
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,290
Chen Hui's father has been

269
00:19:53,290 --> 00:19:55,180
the most honorable man

270
00:19:56,290 --> 00:19:57,770
in this 800-meter radius area.

271
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:03,140
The only thing
he ever wanted to do in life

272
00:20:05,050 --> 00:20:07,420
was to protect the peace here.

273
00:20:09,570 --> 00:20:12,290
Everything you and Hui have done

274
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:15,290
is destroying his faith.

275
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:18,090
That is far crueler
than taking his life.

276
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:22,050
If it were up to Director Chen,

277
00:20:22,050 --> 00:20:24,050
he would rather die with honor

278
00:20:25,330 --> 00:20:26,730
than see you two

279
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:29,050
break the law.

280
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,200
Songge.

281
00:20:35,090 --> 00:20:36,980
Turn yourself in.

282
00:20:37,810 --> 00:20:39,700
There's still time.

283
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,090
Officer Liu.

284
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:51,770
I did everything

285
00:20:51,770 --> 00:20:53,220
all by myself.

286
00:20:54,380 --> 00:20:55,620
Chen Hui was never part of this.

287
00:20:57,330 --> 00:20:59,620
I am the scarred woman
you've been looking for.

288
00:21:00,710 --> 00:21:01,900
I went behind Chen Hui's back,

289
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:02,810
and his parents' too,

290
00:21:02,810 --> 00:21:04,460
to sell cough syrup in Fengyang.

291
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:07,140
I just wanted

292
00:21:07,140 --> 00:21:08,330
to make some extra money.

293
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:09,290
I wanted

294
00:21:09,290 --> 00:21:10,730
to live a little longer.

295
00:21:12,490 --> 00:21:13,460
All the blame

296
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:15,330
falls on me alone.

297
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:17,660
Arrest me

298
00:21:18,450 --> 00:21:19,290
if you must.

299
00:21:19,310 --> 00:21:20,190
Songge.

300
00:21:20,730 --> 00:21:22,860
Wanting to live is never wrong.

301
00:21:25,730 --> 00:21:27,700
But your methods were wrong.

302
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:30,860
And what you did was wrong.

303
00:21:36,490 --> 00:21:38,180
If I could,

304
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:41,180
I would trade my own life

305
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,530
so that Chen Hui's family

306
00:21:42,530 --> 00:21:43,810
could live a good life.

307
00:21:43,810 --> 00:21:44,940
You're wrong.

308
00:21:46,980 --> 00:21:49,090
Only by staying alive

309
00:21:50,570 --> 00:21:51,900
can you pay back the debts

310
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:54,090
you owe in this life.

311
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:56,090
That is the only way

312
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,420
your family can live happily together.

313
00:22:02,490 --> 00:22:03,330
Songge.

314
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:08,620
This is your only chance.

315
00:22:09,770 --> 00:22:10,730
Listen to me.

316
00:22:11,530 --> 00:22:12,420
Turn yourself in.

317
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,330
Even from another world,

318
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:19,810
I will be wishing you all well.

319
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:24,940
I'm going to

320
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:28,330
call Director Chen right now.

321
00:22:29,570 --> 00:22:30,700
You can tell him yourself.

322
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:33,220
Okay?

323
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:42,940
(Cautious)

324
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:01,910
Hello?

325
00:23:03,090 --> 00:23:03,930
Chief Liu.

326
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:05,500
Someone...

327
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:08,940
- Chief Liu?
- Someone...

328
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:11,090
Someone...

329
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:14,050
wants to personally

330
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:17,290
tell you something.

331
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:20,250
Who? Who is it?

332
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:21,090
Tell me what?

333
00:23:26,010 --> 00:23:26,850
Chief Liu?

334
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:29,900
I'm listening, go ahead.

335
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,360
Hello?

336
00:23:39,780 --> 00:23:40,780
Hello? Chief Liu?

337
00:23:41,730 --> 00:23:42,570
Say something!

338
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:59,570
Promise...

339
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:01,770
Promise me...

340
00:24:25,780 --> 00:24:27,900
(Incoming Call: Chen Hongbing)

341
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,180
I'm sorry.

342
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,140
I can't do it.

343
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:48,500
I'm sorry.

344
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:58,100
(People's Public Security)

345
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,390
Alright, everyone settle down.

346
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:11,460
This is

347
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:13,730
Guo Lei, the new Criminal Chief
from the municipal PSB.

348
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:15,010
Starting today,

349
00:25:15,010 --> 00:25:17,380
he will be taking over Liu Na's duties.

350
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,490
Let's welcome him.

351
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:19,330
Welcome.

352
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:23,010
Hello everyone, I'm Guo Lei.

353
00:25:23,010 --> 00:25:24,290
Let's keep this brief.

354
00:25:24,540 --> 00:25:26,090
We just received word.

355
00:25:26,090 --> 00:25:27,660
(Suspect Profile: Tian Jinhai)
Tian Jinhai isn't a foreigner.

356
00:25:28,220 --> 00:25:29,810
He's a Jin'gang local.

357
00:25:29,810 --> 00:25:31,250
He partnered with a friend abroad

358
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:32,730
to run a pharmaceutical company.

359
00:25:32,730 --> 00:25:34,090
Their main business operation

360
00:25:34,090 --> 00:25:35,570
is this Peidun Cough Syrup.

361
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:36,690
We've exchanged information

362
00:25:36,690 --> 00:25:37,700
with the Jin'gang police.

363
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:38,710
A week ago,

364
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,040
Tian Jinhai's partner

365
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,290
was arrested overseas.

366
00:25:41,290 --> 00:25:43,460
Tian Jinhai's inventory in Jin'gang

367
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,620
has also been seized.

368
00:25:45,810 --> 00:25:47,510
Chief Guo, here's the thing.

369
00:25:47,510 --> 00:25:48,940
A few days ago, Tian Jinhai

370
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:50,180
made a trip to

371
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:52,570
the home of Director Chen
of the Fengyang Police Station.

372
00:25:52,570 --> 00:25:54,180
At first, we figured he'd be

373
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,330
hiding around here.

374
00:25:56,530 --> 00:25:57,370
Correct.

375
00:25:57,520 --> 00:25:58,700
However, Tian Jinhai might've

376
00:25:58,700 --> 00:25:59,780
already gotten wind of it.

377
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,580
So our mission now

378
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:02,820
is to work fast

379
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,820
and inspect every hotel.

380
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:07,100
We must find Tian Jinhai.

381
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:08,220
Is that clear?

382
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,060
Understood!

383
00:26:09,340 --> 00:26:10,660
Let's move out.

384
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,500
Yes, sir.

385
00:26:11,940 --> 00:26:12,780
Chief Guo.

386
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:14,380
Thanks for that.
I have a meeting to catch.

387
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:15,220
Alright.

388
00:26:17,620 --> 00:26:18,540
You must be Kang Limin.

389
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,380
Yes, Chief Guo.

390
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:21,220
I am Kang Limin.

391
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,860
I heard Chen Hongbing

392
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:23,860
is your Master.

393
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:24,980
Yes, he is.

394
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:26,860
We'd like to ask
Director Chen for a favor.

395
00:26:26,860 --> 00:26:27,780
Since Tian Jinhai

396
00:26:27,780 --> 00:26:28,620
visited his home,

397
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:31,180
if we manage to catch Tian Jinhai,

398
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:32,700
we'd like him to identify him for us.

399
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:35,140
Chief Guo, since you just got here,

400
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,750
you might not know.

401
00:26:36,890 --> 00:26:37,780
My Master's family...

402
00:26:37,780 --> 00:26:38,620
I know.

403
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:39,660
That's why I need him

404
00:26:39,660 --> 00:26:40,500
to come here,

405
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:41,740
but don't disclose any details.

406
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:43,500
Once we catch the guy,

407
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:44,580
have him ID the suspect.

408
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:47,780
Alright.

409
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:48,940
Chief Guo.

410
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:50,020
I'll find him.

411
00:27:32,060 --> 00:27:33,260
Hello, Mr. Tian.

412
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:35,060
This is the hotel front desk.

413
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:36,180
The letter you wanted to send

414
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:37,380
was dropped off too late.

415
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:38,220
It didn't go out.

416
00:27:38,230 --> 00:27:40,110
We'll send it out first thing
tomorrow morning.

417
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:41,300
Yeah.

418
00:27:41,300 --> 00:27:43,100
Alright, I won't disturb you any further.

419
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:43,940
Goodbye.

420
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,060
- Limin.
- Master.

421
00:28:33,060 --> 00:28:33,940
Something's come up.

422
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:35,220
I need you to come by tomorrow.

423
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:36,140
What is it?

424
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:37,420
I can't talk about it

425
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:38,300
until you get here.

426
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:39,900
What is it this time?

427
00:28:39,900 --> 00:28:40,820
Why so mysterious?

428
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:44,140
By the way, Limin,
there's something else.

429
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,700
Have you seen Chief Liu?

430
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:46,900
No, I haven't.

431
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:47,900
What's wrong, Master?

432
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:49,180
Here's the thing.

433
00:28:49,420 --> 00:28:51,120
She called me just now.

434
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,900
Someone on the phone

435
00:28:52,900 --> 00:28:54,380
wanted to tell me something.

436
00:28:55,020 --> 00:28:55,860
And then,

437
00:28:55,860 --> 00:28:57,020
there was nothing.

438
00:28:57,860 --> 00:28:59,260
When I called back,

439
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:00,300
no one answered.

440
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,620
You should go look for her.

441
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:02,900
See if she needs help.

442
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:04,420
Alright.

443
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:05,980
Don't worry, Master.

444
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,260
I'll have the guys look into it.

445
00:29:07,260 --> 00:29:08,740
You should come to the city first.

446
00:29:08,740 --> 00:29:10,180
Okay. I'm on my way.

447
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:40,860
Hello? Songge?

448
00:29:42,260 --> 00:29:43,140
Chen Hui.

449
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:46,900
Something happened.

450
00:29:48,460 --> 00:29:50,060
Take it easy. Where are you?

451
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:53,540
I'm at the railway bridge.

452
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,260
I'll be right there.

453
00:29:59,500 --> 00:30:06,500
(Cautious)

454
00:30:19,020 --> 00:30:19,860
Songge?

455
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:30,820
I'm here.

456
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:35,940
Officer Liu is gone.

457
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:38,460
She's gone.

458
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:43,500
Still haven't reached Chief Liu?

459
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:44,820
Not yet.

460
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:46,020
We've been calling her,

461
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,380
but she won't answer.

462
00:30:47,380 --> 00:30:49,500
We went to her place last night,
and no one was home.

463
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:51,980
That's weird.

464
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:56,260
Master.

465
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:58,060
I hate to say this,

466
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:00,900
but we should prepare for the worst.

467
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:01,740
I mean it.

468
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,020
What do you mean?

469
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:04,700
Chief Liu hasn't been doing well lately.

470
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:06,380
So I was thinking,

471
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:08,620
maybe she just wanted
to be alone and, you know...

472
00:31:10,100 --> 00:31:11,700
Stop being ridiculous.

473
00:31:30,660 --> 00:31:31,500
Songge.

474
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:32,900
I'm here.

475
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,540
It's going to be okay.

476
00:31:35,980 --> 00:31:37,100
Pull yourself together.

477
00:31:38,300 --> 00:31:39,820
Act like everything is normal.

478
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:41,380
Understand?

479
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:45,660
I understand.

480
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:50,980
I have to go to the hotel
and get that letter back.

481
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,020
Chen Hui.

482
00:32:01,940 --> 00:32:02,780
Be careful.

483
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:05,620
I'll be here waiting.

484
00:32:29,020 --> 00:32:29,860
Master.

485
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:37,380
Chief Guo, this is Director Chen

486
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:39,140
from the Fengyang Police Station.

487
00:32:39,140 --> 00:32:40,340
- Hello, Director Chen.
- Hello.

488
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,860
I'm Guo Lei, from the municipal PSB.

489
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:43,180
I've heard a lot about you.

490
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:44,020
We're all on the same team.

491
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:45,020
No need for formalities.

492
00:32:45,380 --> 00:32:46,220
Chief Guo.

493
00:32:46,220 --> 00:32:47,580
Hold on, let's talk outside.

494
00:32:47,820 --> 00:32:49,900
Director Chen, please wait in the car.

495
00:32:49,900 --> 00:32:50,740
Alright.

496
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:56,980
What's the situation?

497
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:59,970
Tian Jinhai left yesterday afternoon
and hasn't come back.

498
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,210
No one answered his room phone.

499
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:03,310
How many exits at the hotel?

500
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,420
Two.

501
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:05,580
And a loading bay at the back.

502
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:06,500
Let's split up

503
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,340
our tasks at hand.

504
00:33:08,500 --> 00:33:09,580
Si, Chang.

505
00:33:09,580 --> 00:33:10,900
You two cover the back door.

506
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,540
The rest will
follow me through the front.

507
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:13,390
Got it.

508
00:33:13,410 --> 00:33:14,390
Is everybody clear?

509
00:33:25,460 --> 00:33:26,680
Hello, I'm picking up the mail.

510
00:33:27,180 --> 00:33:28,260
Alright, give me a sec.

511
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:31,700
Why didn't Chu come today?

512
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:33,980
He had to take the day off.

513
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,500
You're here pretty early today.

514
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:36,360
All checked.

515
00:33:36,370 --> 00:33:37,250
Thank you.

516
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:41,740
Here you go.

517
00:33:41,740 --> 00:33:42,580
Thanks.
